B.a2n=new A.yR("White Mirror","90 days of radical self-awareness.","A guided journal system for people who are done running from themselves.","Begin",null)
B.a2m=new A.yR("The M.I.R.R.O.R. method.","Six steps. One practice.","Moment. Identify. Reflect. Reframe. Observe. Rise. Every prompt in this journal follows this arc.","Next",null)
B.a2o=new A.yR("Have a journal?","Scan the QR inside the cover.","Your journal contains a unique QR code. Scanning it unlocks the full experience \u2014 all 90 digital companions, AI insights, and your mood map.","I have a journal","Continue without journal")
